Package view.SetupGame

Interface StartGame

All Known Implementing Classes:
LoadGamePanel, NewGamePanel
public interface StartGame
The interface Start game is used in the NewGamePanel and in the LoadGamePanel. The purpose is to define a set of methods that a panel should have to start a game. These methods are implemented in both views.
